{title: Special Characters}

{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[G]Rock & roll is [C]here to stay
[D]Less than < and [G]greater than >
[Am]Quotes both "double" and [Em]'single' too
[F]Ampersands & angle brackets [G]in the queue
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
[G]Backslash \ and [C]forward slash /
[D]Parentheses (like [G]these)
[Am]Square brackets are [Em]for chords
[F]But curly braces [G]are for directives please
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_chorus}
[C]Hash # at @ dollar $
[G]Percent % caret ^
[D]Tilde ~ asterisk * plus +
[G]Equals = and the [C]rest of it
{end_of_chorus}
